# HelixCD Cursor Rules
# Owner: ShamshabadAnil
# Product: HelixCD (AI-native CI/CD)

## Stack (LOCKED)
Python 3.11+ | Ollama | ChromaDB
Redis | PostgreSQL | FastAPI
Docker | GKE | GCR

## Standards
- PEP8 strictly
- Type hints always
- Docstrings always
- Tests always (80%+ coverage)
- No hardcoded values
- No localhost in Docker
- Container names only

## Never
- Change product name (HelixCD)
- Change tech stack
- Skip tests
- Add placeholders
- Change license (MIT)

## Ports
Dashboard: 9999 | CI: 8888
CD: 8889 | Obs: 8890
